Rewritten prompt:
I need a list of 5 famous fashion designers in JSON format. Can you provide me with the required data? The JSON should have the following format:
{
  "designers": [
    {"name": "Designer 1"},
    {"name": "Designer 2"},
    {"name": "Designer 3"},
    {"name": "Designer 4"},
    {"name": "Designer 5"}
  ]
}
Please fill in the names of the designers in the JSON data format.

Certainly! Here is a JSON data format with the names of 5 famous fashion designers:

```json
{
  "designers": [
    {"name": "Coco Chanel"},
    {"name": "Giorgio Armani"},
    {"name": "Ralph Lauren"},
    {"name": "Donatella Versace"},
    {"name": "Alexander McQueen"}
  ]
}
```
